# "Det var en gang" — starter tempo setup (auto-loaded next to the score).
# Score says Swing quarter = 120; swing itself is Phase 4, so judge sync
# on beat-aligned material only (see the Phase 3 checklist).
#
# Positions: <float beats> | m<n> | m<n>+<beats>  (measure numbers are
# safest — the 2/4 bars m5/m14 make raw beat arithmetic error-prone).

offset 0.77   # TUNE THIS FIRST: seconds of audio before m1 beat 1.
              # It also absorbs any constant output/decoder latency.
m1 126        # then refine; live players rarely sit exactly at 120.

# Only if drift becomes visible, add corrections at section starts:
